{
  "stem": "17135.6",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went to junior college because also I had no matriculation, but I went six years to-- to gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We learned more than here with matriculation, believe me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I-- I went to the Jewish Federation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had a job-finding committee there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, here, here, here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah. yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My-- my sister lived-- my brother lived in New York.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said, you go to live-- and they would be happier there than New York.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "New York was-- was a mess then.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyway, so they find me a job in the garment industry.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The garment industry was, at that time, 99% Jewish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I started as nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And after a year, I took the whole company.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And then, then I went to school and I made a Master's degree, an MBA.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I joined a-- a very fashionable firm.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Ernst Strauss.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They made-- one of the finest suit company in the United States.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then I became a partner.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I bought the company.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because they were-- they want to retire, the other two partners.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then I, myself, retired, in '93.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I closed up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Enough.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Look, let me tell you something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After i went so many times to Germany to testify, I realize how important it is, that the world will know what happened.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At that time, nobody wanted to hear about the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was in Germany in-- in the late '50s, and in the '60s.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The American Jewry was interested in-- in the world, in the Holocaust after the TV series.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then, in the Eichmann Trial, that somehow woke up the world that the holocaust was just not a massacre.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was a watershed event in human history.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I got very active.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was active in Israel too, in Holocaust causes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
